body_html:
I got the exactly same error.
caffe2 was installed via conda install with pre-built on the following conda and python version

  • conda version is 4.5.8
  • conda python version 3.6.5

After checking of make_mnist_db executable, included in caffe2 installed by conda install pre-built,
The root cause might be discrepancy of python versions between the pre-build caffe2(may be based on python2) and my python environment (python 3.6.5)

I have tested the tutorial with caffe2 pre-build and python2 environment but get the same error.
Hence I don't think that python version does affect the current issue.

body:
I got the exactly same error.
caffe2 was installed via conda install with pre-built on the following conda and python version
- conda version is 4.5.8
- conda python version 3.6.5

After checking of `make_mnist_db` executable, included in caffe2 installed by conda install pre-built, 
The root cause might be discrepancy of python versions between the pre-build  caffe2(may be based on python2) and  my python environment (python 3.6.5)

I have tested the tutorial with caffe2 pre-build  and  python2 environment but get the same error. 
Hence I don't think that python version does affect the current issue.
